\section{Database survey}
Details of the comprehensive literature search for citrate structures are presented in Rammohan \& Kaduk (2018). The powder pattern of $\mathrm{K}_{2} \mathrm{RbC}_{6} \mathrm{H}_{5} \mathrm{O}_{7}\left(\mathrm{H}_{2} \mathrm{O}\right)$ was indexed on a primitive monoclinic unit cell having $a=7.2676, b=11.8499, c$

